name: PRECISION
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Murmuration. Moving in flow together, dancing in bliss.

Have you ever had a moment when you knew you were in flow? Dancing from one movement to the next with an elegant precision. Creating a piece of music or artwork, cooking a meal or
having a conversation?

There is something coming together with others where you are concerned.
Get ready for an experience of beautiful flow together. 

Precision is a hallmark of the flow state, things just land correctly and fit with ease. Watch starlings murmuring all in sync flying precise movements in the spontaneous expression of flow together. Nature is abundantly expressive and dramatically beautiful. Humans can also access flow states and when this happens with others we know why we are social creatures and how we can enhance each others lives by finding how we can flow 
together.
